10#include <stdio.h>
11#include "internal/cryptlib.h"
12#include <openssl/asn1t.h>
13#include <openssl/x509.h>
14#include "internal/x509_int.h"
15
16ASN1_SEQUENCE(X509_SIG) = {
17 ASN1_SIMPLE(X509_SIG, algor, X509_ALGOR),
18 ASN1_SIMPLE(X509_SIG, digest, ASN1_OCTET_STRING)
19} ASN1_SEQUENCE_END(X509_SIG)
20
21IMPLEMENT_ASN1_FUNCTIONS(X509_SIG)
22
23void X509_SIG_get0(const X509_SIG *sig, const X509_ALGOR **palg,
24 const ASN1_OCTET_STRING **pdigest)
25{
26 if (palg)
27 *palg = sig->algor;
28 if (pdigest)
29 *pdigest = sig->digest;
30}
31
32void X509_SIG_getm(X509_SIG *sig, X509_ALGOR **palg,
33 ASN1_OCTET_STRING **pdigest)
34{
35 if (palg)
36 *palg = sig->algor;
37 if (pdigest)
38 *pdigest = sig->digest;
39}
